data.description: Welcome to your new home nestled in the heart of Lindale ISD! This charming property boasts a perfect blend of comfort, style, and outdoor allure. Step inside to discover a spacious open-concept layout where the living room seamlessly flows into the kitchen area, creating an inviting space for both daily living and entertaining. The kitchen features ample cabinet space, and a convenient breakfast nook overlooking the living room and wood burning fireplace. With three bedrooms and two baths, including a master suite with its own private bath, this home offers plenty of room for relaxation and privacy. Each bedroom is generously sized and filled with natural light, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. Outside, you'll find a backyard oasis awaiting your enjoyment. The fully fenced yard provides privacy and security, while the expansive .583 acre lot offers plenty of space for outdoor activities and gardening. The highlight of the outdoor space is the wonderful deck and patio area, perfect for hosting gatherings with friends and family or simply unwinding after a long day.Located in the highly desirable Lindale ISD, this home offers the perfect blend of tranquility and convenience. Whether you're enjoying the peaceful surroundings or exploring the nearby amenities, you'll love calling this place home. Don't miss your chance to make this lovely property yours!
